<div class="logo-transition" id="logo-transition" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="brand-logo-image" src="/assets/conneen-ai-logo.png" alt="" />
  </div>

  <section class="site-shell" id="site-shell" aria-label="Conneen AI Consulting website">
    <header class="site-header">
      <a class="brand-lockup site-brand" href="#top" aria-label="Conneen AI Consulting home">
        <img class="brand-logo-image" src="/assets/conneen-ai-logo.png" alt="Conneen AI Consulting" />
      </a>

      <nav class="site-nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        <button class="site-nav-button" id="return-chat-button" type="button">
          Return to chatbot
        </button>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="site-main" id="top">
      <section class="hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="section-kicker">Practical AI systems for real operations</p>
          <h2>Turn messy workflows into measurable gains.</h2>
          <p>
            Conneen AI builds AI, automation, analytics, and custom software systems for businesses that need less manual drag, better information flow, and tools people can actually use.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="site-button primary" href="mailto:wiwyco@gmail.com">Start a consultation</a>
            <a class="site-button" href="#services">Explore services</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="consulting-panel" aria-label="Consulting interface preview">
          <div class="panel-top">
            <p class="panel-label">Consulting interface</p>
            <p class="panel-title">Find the highest-leverage AI pilot.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="signal-list">
            <div class="signal-item">
              <span class="signal-num">01</span>
              <span>
                <strong>Map the bottleneck</strong>
                Quote work, reporting, scheduling, intake, document review, or data entry.
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="signal-item">
              <span class="signal-num">02</span>
              <span>
                <strong>Connect the knowledge</strong>
                Bring together spreadsheets, forms, files, emails, and business rules.
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="signal-item">
              <span class="signal-num">03</span>
              <span>
                <strong>Build a practical pilot</strong>
                Keep expert review in the loop while removing repetitive work.
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="about">
        <p class="section-kicker">About</p>
        <h3>Hands-on AI consulting without layers of sales overhead.</h3>
        <p>
          Conneen AI is built around direct, engineering-first consulting. The goal is not vague AI strategy; it is identifying where AI and automation can improve throughput, reliability, and decision support inside real business workflows.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="services">
        <p class="section-kicker">Services</p>
        <h3>From strategy to implementation.</h3>
        <div class="cards">
          <article class="card">
            <strong>AI strategy development</strong>
            <p>Identify where AI can support business objectives, reduce bottlenecks, and create a focused implementation roadmap.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <strong>Model implementation</strong>
            <p>Integrate AI into existing processes through assistants, automations, custom applications, and data workflows.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <strong>Training & support</strong>
            <p>Help teams understand, operate, and improve the AI tools they depend on while keeping human judgment in the loop.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <strong>Data analysis and insights</strong>
            <p>Turn operational data into dashboards, forecasts, reports, and decision-ready signals.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <strong>Automation solutions</strong>
            <p>Replace repetitive manual steps with reliable workflows across documents, forms, spreadsheets, and internal systems.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <strong>Custom AI solutions</strong>
            <p>Build tailored assistants and software systems around your company knowledge, constraints, and review process.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="contact">
        <p class="section-kicker">Contact</p>
        <h3>Let’s explore AI solutions together.</h3>
        <p>
          Send a note, call, or use the chatbot to shape your first pilot idea before booking a deeper consultation.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-grid">
          <div class="contact-card">
            <div class="contact-row">
              <span>Phone</span>
              <a href="tel:+19072098799">907-209-8799</a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-row">
              <span>Email</span>
              <a href="mailto:wiwyco@gmail.com">wiwyco@gmail.com</a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-row">
              <span>Location</span>
              <span>5851 Sargassum Lane, Milton, FL 32583 US</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-card">
            <strong>Hours</strong>
            <div class="hours-grid" aria-label="Business hours">
              <span>Monday</span><span>9:00am – 5:00pm</span>
              <span>Tuesday</span><span>9:00am – 5:00pm</span>
              <span>Wednesday</span><span>9:00am – 5:00pm</span>
              <span>Thursday</span><span>9:00am – 5:00pm</span>
              <span>Friday</span><span>9:00am – 5:00pm</span>
              <span>Saturday</span><span>9:00am – 5:00pm</span>
              <span>Sunday</span><span>9:00am – 5:00pm</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
